  pages    = "1101--1108",
  abstract = "We investigated ethnic differences in spirometry and gas transfer
              (DL(CO)) in a young, healthy population of nonsmoking physicians
              and medical students aged 22-33 yr, of European or Asian descent.
              Each answered questions detailing ethnic background, medical
              history, level of physical activity, and length of residence in
